# ðŸ¢ Real-World Business Problem Solved

## The Traditional Travel Booking Problem:

| Challenge | Impact |
|-----------|--------|
| Physical visit required | Customers must visit travel agency in person |
| Limited browsing | Paper catalogs, limited information |
| Manual booking process | Phone calls, paperwork, errors |
| Payment friction | Cash/cheque, no instant confirmation |
