| Poor tracking | No real-time booking status |

## How E-TOUR Solves These Problems:

| Solution | Benefit |
|----------|---------|
| **Web-based platform** | Access from anywhere, anytime |
| **Rich tour catalog** | Detailed descriptions, images, pricing |
| **Self-service booking** | Browse â†’ Select â†’ Book in minutes |
| **Online payments** | Secure Razorpay integration |
| **Real-time status** | Instant booking confirmation |
| **Personal dashboard** | View bookings, download invoices |

